Character code independent files have been installed.  Now, install
either japanese/ptex-jis, japanese/ptex-euc or japanese/ptex-sjis.

Note that name of these packages indicates the character code used for
the output to the terminal and log files.  The following table shows
which character code is used for different purposes.

          ptex-euc   ptex-sjis  ptex-jis
Internal  EUC        SJIS       EUC
Input     EUC/JIS    SJIS/JIS   JIS/EUC
Output    EUC        SJIS       JIS
DVI       JIS        JIS        JIS

